Language name: TIDDIM CHIN
Language number: 2513
Alternate names: Kamhau
Classification: Sino-Tibetan, Kuki-Naga
Comments: Tiddim Chin is spoken in Chin Hills, Tiddim area 
in Burma.

Sources: 

Henderson, E.J. 1965. Tiddim Chin: A Descriptive Analysis 
